+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Simple Student                                              Version 0.1 |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| WHAT IS SIMPLE STUDENT?                                                 |
| Simple Student is a program created in Python that is designed to       |
| manage students, teachers, and courses for a school. Not only can it    |
| keep track of this information, but it can create student schedules     |
| based off stored records.                                               |
